text: Eliana Maria Nagib Aleixo is a retired volleyball player from Brazil. Eliana competed at the 1980 Summer Olympics. She was born on 13 July 1954.Eliana Aleixo == References == Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian volleyball players Category:Olympians for Brazil Category:Sportspeople from Belo Horizonte
